The paper focuses on image retrieval using free-hand sketches, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed method involves deep learning techniques, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of auxiliary sketch-tokens to mitigate geometric distortion, which involves some level of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
